metadata.name: Life inside supercomputers
metadata.description:
The story starts here when supercomputers overtook the world. People constructed advanced civilizations with the purpose of living in harmony with the machines. The symbiosis of organic life and circuitry.

This artwork is the second piece for “Life inside Supercomputer”. The story continues.                                                                                                                             Life inside supercomputers 02
